729506f-a.folder: Richmond Terrace & Houseman Avenue, Staten Island, NY
729506f-a.text:
2640 Richmond Terrace, adjoining the S.W. corner ef Houseman Avenue. Beers's map of 1874, and Rebinson's maps of 1898 and 1907 show it te have been the Herry Miller house.
September 28, 1924.
Wm. T. Davis through P.L. Sperr
